---

## 1. Project Overview

This repository contains two microservices:

### UserManagementService (UMS)
- Handles registration, login, authentication, and token issuing.

### YuhanTweetService (TS)
- Allows authenticated users to publish tweets, follow producers, and retrieve messages.

**Technologies used:**  
Java 17, Spring Boot WebFlux (Netty), REST API, MySQL 8.

---

## 2. Repository Structure

Assignment 4/  
├── Assignment4_YAML/  
├── Diagrams/  
├── UserManagementService/  
├── YuhanTweetService/  
├── .gitignore  
├── README.md  
└── thunder_collection.json

---

## 3. How to Build

Run the following command inside each service directory: mvn clean install

---

## 4. How to Run the Services

### UserManagementService
Port: **8080**  
Command: mvn spring-boot:run

### YuhanTweetService
Port: **8082**  
Command: mvn spring-boot:run


---

## 5. API Testing Instructions

### 1) Register User
POST  
http://localhost:8081/api/register

### 2) Login User (returns token)
POST  
http://localhost:8081/api/login

### 3) Create Tweet
POST  
http://localhost:8082/tweets  
Required header:  
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### 4) Get All Producers
GET  
http://localhost:8082/producers

### 5) Get Messages by Producer
GET  
http://localhost:8082/messages/producer/{id}

### 6) Get Messages Visible to Subscriber
GET  
http://localhost:8082/messages/subscriber/{id}

---

